Package: cpeat
Type: Package
Title: Peatland decomposition and carbon models
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Paul Tansley
Maintainer: Paul Tansley  <pt360@exeter.ac.uk>
Description: A collection of various peatland decompositon and carbon dynamics models. 
    These are the Clymo 1984 (clymo) model, the 'peatland decompostion model' (pdm), developed by Frolking et al,
    and the'super peatland' model (mega_bog) developed by Zicheng Yu.
    
    Clymo model: https://doi.org/10.1098/rstb.1984.0002
    Peatland Decomposition model: https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10021-001-0105-1
    Super Peatland model: https://doi.org/10.1177/0959683610386982
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: tidyverse
    imputeTS
    forestmangr
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
